# Claude Code / agent skills
# .agents/skills/ holds skill content; .claude/skills/<name> symlinks point
# into it. Hand-authored (native) skills ARE committed. Vendored skills are
# tracked only via skills-lock.json — their content is restored with
# `npx skills experimental_install`, so their dirs are ignored below (add one
# line per vendored skill you install). .gitattributes marks .agents as
# linguist-vendored to keep it out of language stats.
.agents/skills/cubepi/
.agents/skills/cubepi-trace/
.agents/skills/playwright-cli/
.agents/skills/web-design-guidelines/
.superpowers/
settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
backend/.claude/


